Class MazeGenerator

java.lang.Object
  MazeGenerator

public class MazeGenerator
extends java.lang.Object

A class that generate a maze with depth first search algorithm. Generate a maze without starting & exit point.

Author:
floren

createMaze

private void createMaze(int currX,
                        int currY)
Create a maze (collection of Tile objects). Tile has south, north, east, and west boundary. true in the boundary means there is no wall between 2 tiles.

Parameters:
currX - number of tiles in x dimension.
currY - number of tiles in y dimension.
